.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, hiking, video-games
4 different games are played: poker, go, snooker, domino
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, mouse, turtle
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the left of the person playing poker##8
 2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the person playing snooker is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person playing snooker is somewhere between the person playing domino and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games and the person playing poker have different parity positions##9
 6. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
 7. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 9. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing poker##1
10. the owner of the bird is between the person playing poker and the owner of the turtle##2
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the person playing poker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | video-games | hiking     | drawing  | fishing |
| Nationality   | go       | poker    | snooker | domino |
| Pet           | mouse       | guinea-pig | bird     | turtle  |

